snippet.title: Battle Gem Ponies - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Check Out BGP on Kickstarter: http://bit.ly/3r4uzGU 
And subscribe to keep up with the game's development!

The campaign will be ongoing Aug 3rd - Sep 3rd
Follow Us wherever you happen to hang out: https://linktr.ee/YotesGames


It's been a wild ride so far, and it's about to get even wilder.
We can't wait to blast through our goals and get this game into your hands!
